{"tid":807933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍想奪台？國防部：只能登上外島","createTime":"2018-09-06T02:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T04:43:13.000Z","uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7e0048d3016e808281128d21e0fd672dc6f6ea46","tid":807933,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T02:43:45.000Z","msg":"日前陸媒貼出了一張解放軍乘坐登陸艇從北市淡水河登陸的照片，不過這合成照實在太失真，就連中國大陸的網友也都看不下去。但以目前解放軍的戰力，真的能夠登陸台灣本島，進行登陸作戰嗎？對此，國防部日前也公布了「五年兵力整建及施政計畫報告」，直接打臉陸媒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/e3_dbRX26GbZYqcdItAAXQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/78c21c2ab84f1664ac3c04dc2587f33c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fe3_dbRX26GbZYqcdItAAXQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F78c21c2ab84f1664ac3c04dc2587f33c&h=12130e9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲陸媒日前貼出一張合成圖，氣墊船長驅直入淡水河。（圖／翻攝自微博）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中共解放軍始終不放棄以武力犯台，各種心戰作為不斷，甚至還派出軍艦、軍機繞台，不但影響台灣民眾，甚至試圖動搖台灣軍心。《新浪》軍事網在8月10日刊登「木罌夜半飛渡軍 解放軍野馬氣墊船如何在台灣海峽狂飆」文章，並附上一張解放軍登陸艇從淡水河長驅直入的合成照。<span style=\"color: red;\">但貽笑大方的是，整張圖的比例失真，就連陸網友也紛紛吐槽。</span><br />\n<br />\n至於解放軍目前的實力是否已達到合成照所示，能登陸台灣島進行作戰？國防部也在「五年兵力整建及施政計畫報告」中指出，解放軍對於侵台採取三階段，劃分戰役籌劃、聯合火力打擊、登陸作戰，目前解放軍雖已具備聯合火力打擊，但要登陸本島還有難度。因為要登陸台灣本島，除了要具備完善的輸運能力外，還得靠龐大的後勤支援，目前解放軍頂多僅有「奪我外島、離島」的登陸作戰能力。（編輯：林奇樺）"},{"pid":"3dd44cbdce85609cf68b1b2ddecca7acb8202410","tid":807933,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T02:52:33.000Z","msg":"投放核彈炸撚死班台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be386690434adc9349dd75f5fdff709d97521e62","tid":807933,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T02:57:53.000Z","msg":"早就放棄金馬"},{"pid":"04a532580b96d6d60961629dd823cf4623c6298d","tid":807933,"uid":25673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:13:49.000Z","msg":"衰撚過小畫家"},{"pid":"1bf137228e2e038f01b05a24c7b87149d636de25","tid":807933,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:15:47.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2564b06a4b32f490071fde266b57a1c1dadca89d","tid":807933,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bf137228e2e038f01b05a24c7b87149d636de25","tid":807933,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:15:47.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:20:47.000Z","msg":"證明支那氣墊船,可以上陸地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c837795180b0544af46a8c1b211e84f52ee163","tid":807933,"uid":200328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:32:21.000Z","msg":"咁撚大架登陸艇<br />\n打撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee491e6693c6786255621f4aeab6cfcaf817cc5","tid":807933,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"張相咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecb8de2a614a6a880d96641a875f09c96ce101c","tid":807933,"uid":90321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:43:13.000Z","msg":"洗撚真打咩，到時打個電話，大把共諜同國民黨係台灣裡應外合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}